          "id": "6",
          "speaker": "Origin_Intro_Gale",
          "text": "You find yourself in the presence of the renowned wizarding prodigy, Gale of Waterdeep - please, no need to be intimidated.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Confident, slightly pompous tone - trying to impress you, even if he pretends otherwise",
          "checkflags": [],
